references: Repealing: Ord 2406, Ord 3466, Ord 3421, Ord 3830, Ord 4000, Ord 4005
summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 2406, entitled "An Ordinance to carry out the intent and enforce the provisions of Article X of the City Charter relating to the health of the City", approved November 4, 1892, and Ordinance No. 3466, approved July 25, 1894, No. 3421, approved June 25, 1894, and No. 3830, approved May 28, 1895, and No. 4005, approved November 9, 1895 and No. 4000, approved November 7, 1895, amendatory thereof.
